NAME
    Perinci::CmdLine::Lite::Patch::ShowArgsBeforeValidation - Patch
    Perinci::CmdLine::Lite's hook_before_action() to show arguments before
    validation

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.002 of
    Perinci::CmdLine::Lite::Patch::ShowArgsBeforeValidation (from Perl
    distribution Perinci-CmdLine-Lite-Patch-ShowArgsBeforeValidation),
    released on 2020-01-01.

SYNOPSIS
     % PERL5OPT=-MPerinci::CmdLine::Lite::Patch::ShowArgsBeforeValidation yourscript.pl ...

DESCRIPTION
    This patch can be used for debugging.

